body:
@tangjeff0 agreed.
- The highlight was supposed to be black according to the mockups, so a little bit darker and clearer, but I wasn't able to get them to change on row hover until just now. That's fixed in the cleanup PR. Open to discussing more contrast.
- Until we're able to trim the string, this is a tradeoff between sometimes clipping out the term and sometimes just seeing enormous block previews. Clipping to 1 line is probably overzealous, so I'll show the whole result until a decision is made or the trimming feature is added.
